       These two things are the same.

================================================================================

CHAPTERS

${rozdzialy.map(r => `  ${String(r.data.order).padStart(2, '0')}. ${r.data.title}
      ${r.data.description || ''}
      URL: https://776f6c6e6f.org/rozdzial/${r.id}
`).join('\n')}

================================================================================

